{
  "stem": "22582.5",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "Roosevelt was my uncle.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And so that was about a few days later that we escaped, about three or four days later that must have been.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And I was liberated, I believe-- I don't know exactly what day I was liberated.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "I was about 12, 13 days in the woods.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "Every time we found a place and-- and we got [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] to the-- they had kept chickens, for instance.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "They had this very small place where they kept the chicken.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "And they had a little bit of hay, and we went.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "We got inside.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "And-- and in the morning, the woman came in to look for the eggs, and they found us.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "And so she got scared.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "And then we were supposed to-- you just go further.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "We just-- and she'd actually-- they all-- they all got scared that we were the prisoners.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "And they didn't know.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "I imagine they were scared of the Germans.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "They were scared of us.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we were going down by-- by-- by night.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We were walking.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And in the morning, usually they-- they caught us somehow.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And once when we went there, we stopped and they were where the forester had a house.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] he was a Pole, I remember.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Oh, he said, he's going to help us.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "He's going to help us.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Don't worry.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Everything is all right.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "You are safe here.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "You are safe here.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "All of a sudden, he disappeared.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then we were suspicious.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then we went to the-- to the-- didn't want to stay in the-- in the barrack.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we came and he came with a Germans somehow.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So I don't know what happened, because one of the Czech boy-- man-- was already sick.",
      "word_count": 16
    }
  ],
